title: IAA Tonight | Fallout From Ime Udoka's Suspension AND Previewing the NFL Weekend
description: The Boston Celtics have suspended Head Coach Ime Udoka for the 2022-23 season and cited violations of team policies in their statement. Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly and Auntie Chantel Tremetiere react to the news and what this means for the franchise. Plus, there is a good slate of NFL games this weekend, including Tom Brady vs. Aaron Rodgers as the Tampa Bay Buccaneers are set to face the Green Bay Packers on Sunday. Find out their predictions on that game and more!
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Chantel Tremetiere)
